## 3. Missing Components Identified

- **Authentication/Security layer** for agent actions (no agent should execute OS commands without approval)
- **Audit log / action ledger** — every action must be traceable
- **Plugin/Skill registry** — how new capabilities are added at runtime
- **Human-in-the-loop (HITL) gateway** — approval flow for destructive actions
- **Observability stack** — metrics, tracing, health dashboards
- **Sandboxed execution environment** — for Coder Brain to safely run generated code
- **Configuration management** — how modules discover each other
- **Graceful degradation** — what happens when a brain/agent fails

