## 11. MYTHOS Foundation Model — Phased Plan

> System remains functional without MYTHOS. It uses Ollama (Llama 3 / Mistral) as the default LLM backend.

| Phase | Milestone | Description |
|-------|-----------|-------------|
| M-1 | Tokenizer | SentencePiece BPE tokenizer trained on domain corpus |
| M-2 | Mini Transformer | 125M param decoder-only GPT in PyTorch |
| M-3 | Training Pipeline | DataLoader, optimizer, checkpointing |
| M-4 | Dataset Pipeline | Crawl4AI + cleaning + dedup pipeline |
| M-5 | Reasoning Dataset | Chain-of-thought, tool-use, agent-task data |
| M-6 | Foundation V1 | 1B param model, basic reasoning |
| M-7 | Foundation V2 | 3B param, RDT layers (OpenMythos-inspired) |
| M-8 | Agent-Centric Training | Fine-tune on JARVIS agent interaction traces |
| M-9 | Evaluation Framework | JARVIS-Bench: memory, planning, tool-use evals |
| M-10 | Continuous Improvement | RLHF-lite loop using agent feedback |

