## 15. Risk Assessment

| Risk | Severity | Probability | Mitigation |
|------|----------|-------------|------------|
| Hardware insufficient for MYTHOS training | HIGH | HIGH | Use LoRA fine-tuning on existing SLM; defer pretraining |
| Agent coordination deadlocks | HIGH | MEDIUM | LangGraph timeout + circuit breakers |
| Self-improvement introduces regressions | HIGH | MEDIUM | Branch-test-benchmark gate; never auto-merge |
| Memory inconsistency (Neo4j / Qdrant drift) | MEDIUM | MEDIUM | Sync validator runs hourly |
| Whisper.cpp latency unacceptable | MEDIUM | LOW | Fall back to faster-whisper or Vosk |
| Neo4j Community Edition limits | LOW | LOW | FalkorDB is a drop-in alternative |
| OpenMythos RDT instability | MEDIUM | HIGH | Use standard GPT-2 architecture for MYTHOS V1 |
| DESi integration unclear | HIGH | HIGH | Remove DESi; replaced by OpenHands |
| Voice model MisoTTS hardware req. | MEDIUM | MEDIUM | Fall back to Piper TTS (much lighter) |
| Scope creep stalling Phase 1 | HIGH | HIGH | Strict phase gates; no Phase N+1 until N tests pass |

